body_html: @qinyao-he There could be many reasons but it is not possible to figure out what is wrong from the pictures since only parent scopes are visible in the plots but not the nodes themselves. Would it be possible to share the network? At least some logs? Also for the time being, TFTRT requires shapes to be statically inferable at the conversion time. Are your non-batch input ranks fixed or are the free?
